                  ### üìä Twoje aktywno≈õci Strava
                  
                  **Ostatni bieg:** {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_run') }}
                  - üìÖ {{ as_timestamp(states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_run_date')) | timestamp_custom('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M') }}
                  - üèÉ {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_run_distance') | float | round(1) }} km
                  - ‚è±Ô∏è {% set seconds = states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_run_moving_time') | int %}{{ (seconds // 3600) }}:{{ '%02d' | format((seconds % 3600) // 60) }}:{{ '%02d' | format(seconds % 60) }}
                  - ‚ù§Ô∏è {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_run_average_heartrate') | float | round(1) }} bpm
                  - üëç {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_run_kudos') }} kudos
                  
                  **Ostatnia jazda:** {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_ride') }}
                  - üìÖ {{ as_timestamp(states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_ride_date')) | timestamp_custom('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M') }}
                  - üö¥ {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_ride_distance') | float | round(1) }} km
                  - ‚è±Ô∏è {% set seconds = states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_ride_moving_time') | int %}{{ (seconds // 3600) }}:{{ '%02d' | format((seconds % 3600) // 60) }}:{{ '%02d' | format(seconds % 60) }}
                  - ‚¨ÜÔ∏è {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_ride_elevation_gain') | float | round(1) }} m
                  - üëç {{ states('sensor.strava_igor_wojcik_ride_kudos') }} kudos
                  
